{"tid":2130532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"巴塞叛徒高層執意趕走忠心球員並告上法庭","createTime":"2020-07-29T09:03:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:28:02.000Z","uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa050f533a1018be5da877236570eaad22cf1046","tid":2130532,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:03:51.000Z","msg":"據西班牙媒體報導，巴塞隆拿將起訴巴西球星美路。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n23歲的美路拒絕為巴塞出戰歐冠盃，擅自回到了巴西，對此，巴塞球會打算採用法律手段。《馬卡報》稱，巴塞方面的律師已經準備好了起訴文件，球會方面也將對美路進行內部處罰。<br />\n<br />\n美路認為遭到了巴塞的不公對待，<span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"medium\"><span class=\"red\">他之前多次表態不想離隊</span></span></span>，但最終被強迫轉會祖雲達斯。但球會認為，美路的行為是背叛和缺乏職業精神，鬧到這一步，只有通過法律手段解決。<br />\n<br />\n個topic應該如此，新浪仲屈人背叛"},{"pid":"3a476f74022d68f86a031d95b5234025ae3833d0","tid":2130532,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"點逼 死都唔同祖記簽合約咪得"},{"pid":"b8f95189c69b1807ed94000d845a12ae2fe2c4d2","tid":2130532,"uid":134997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b961868c1b493e2acf70b1a5d0ae150601d8ebf3","tid":2130532,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"轉會官宣完一場西甲都冇得出<br />\n而家仲想佢返去操波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a63c808ccad4fe73aa1fd309e168afb2ebd7e1d4","tid":2130532,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8f95189c69b1807ed94000d845a12ae2fe2c4d2","tid":2130532,"uid":134997,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3a476f74022d68f86a031d95b5234025ae3833d0","tid":2130532,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:10:10.000Z","msg":"點逼 死都唔同祖記簽合約咪得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:39:10.000Z","msg":"佢一個禮拜人工頂你幾年啦"},{"pid":"ff63e0318240d7a818f633db7f48a08f0b9d6764","tid":2130532,"uid":90515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c